rows.label: tlk42200121_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Popipii came to this city on a trip, mo!
I think it's a great, lively city, mo!

rows.label: tlk42200121_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Popipii saw a wonderful sight on the
way here, mo!

rows.label: tlk42200121_01_msg0003
rows.name:
A Driver extended a hand to another Driver
who had fallen and helped them up, mo.

rows.label: tlk42200121_01_msg0004
rows.name:
When a friend falls, you go to them
and lend a hand...

rows.label: tlk42200121_01_msg0005
rows.name:
Friends are wonderful, mo!
That was a moment more beautiful than any work of art, mo!
